OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784465300
OL,3,CBurnham will be first PM for 50 years
OL,4,Cwith seat in north-west England
OL,6,FAndy Burnham will be the first prime
OL,7,Fminister for 50 years to represent a
OL,8,Fconstituency in the north-west of
OL,9,FEngland and only the third premier
OL,10,Fsince 1900 to hold a seat in the
OL,11,Fregion.
OL,13,FMr Burnham became member of parliament
OL,14,Ffor Makerfield in Greater Manchester a
OL,15,Ffew weeks ago, after winning a by-
OL,16,Felection on 18 June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
